        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &quot;Sagar Samman Award- Sagar Samman Award for Excellence&quot; scheme has been launched by the Ministry of Ports, Shipping and Waterways under the Directorate General of Shipping, Government of India, aims to recognize consistently high-quality contributions in the maritime sector. Under this scheme, a prestigious award is provided to individuals demonstrating excellence in leadership, innovation, and sector development.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Ship Model\n- Citation Certificate\n- National recognition\n\n<br>\n\n",
